longBusinessSummary: InVision Aktiengesellschaft, together with its subsidiaries, develops and markets products and services in the field of workforce management and education in Europe and the United States. The company offers products, such as injixo, a cloud-based workforce management software to optimize workforce planning process; and The Call Center School, a cloud-based e-learning solution. It serves contact centers, small businesses, and large corporations. The company was formerly known as InVision Software AG and changed its name to InVision Aktiengesellschaft in August 2012. InVision Aktiengesellschaft was founded in 1995 and is headquartered in DÃ¼sseldorf, Germany.
